''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''
' This Module is the basis for all other files in this library, as it is the errorhandler for all possible errors
' It works like this:
' If an Error occures for the first time since execution it will initialize all errormessages
' Then it will get the message by defined parameters
' It will show the message at the immediate window or MsgBox + immediate window
' Considering the severity of the error the program might close all execution
''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''

